<h2>Bleeding, Blood or red colored urine and Vaginal bleeding between periods</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms bleeding, blood or red colored urine and vaginal bleeding between periods including Hemophilia, Medication reaction or side-effect, and Urinary tract infection (UTI).</p>
<p>There  are 22 conditions  associated with bleeding, blood or red colored urine and vaginal bleeding between periods. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
